Title: h3GetIndexesFromUnidirectionalEdge
Description: Returns the origin and destination hexagon indexes from the given unidirectional edge H3Index.
edge — Hexagon index number that represents a unidirectional edge. UInt64.
A tuple consisting of two values tuple(origin,destination):
origin — Origin Hexagon index number. UInt64.destination — Destination Hexagon index number. UInt64.
Returns (0,0) if the provided input is not valid.
